HEADWORD: Signalman
<hw>Sig"nal*man</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>-men</plw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <def>A man whose business is to
